New in EB real estate: this $250k houseboat in Rockaway Beach, NY 🚤 

Located in one of the most sought-after slips in New York City at Marina 59, the 1968 Gibson Riverboat is a perfect summer beach pad for surfers, artists, fishermen or as an investment property. Features include:

🌊 One bedroom, one bathroom houseboat;
🔥 Cozy wood pellet stove (plus electric heat) for chilly weather;
🛁 Full kitchen and bathroom;
🛋️ Separate office/sitting room;
☀️ Upper deck located off generously sized bedroom;
🎣 Two lower level decks;
Private parking;
🚤 No property tax & low $642 slip fee (Marina dues) per month;
🚊 Two blocks from the A train.

Grab this one of a kind houseboat before summer begins to escape the city beat and enjoy the beach life at Far Rockaway. Interested buyers may rent the houseboat for a discounted rate leading up to the sale; inquire with listing agent for info. 

‼️ Open house Sunday, March 19 2-3:30 pm at Marina 59.

Listed by Fon Tongsomboon with Re/Max Elite. For showing or inquiries, contact Fon Tongsomboon at 347-640-3560 or fonremax@gmail.com.

New in EB real estate: the Sylvan, a design-forward, climate-friendly home in Glen Spey, NY.

This sunny home with a private guest studio space was completed in 2023 by @wishbonedesignbuild. Features include:

🏠 Three bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home;
🌿 1,937 square foot new build on 3.44 acres;
⚡️ All new utilities including septic, well, and electric;
🛁 Primary bedroom ensuite with soaking tub, walk-in shower, double sink and heated floors;
🍴Chef’s kitchen with brand new appliances;
🔥 Living room with picture windows, high efficiency wood stove;
☀️ 525 square foot expansive sundeck; 
⛽️ A two-car carport with an EV charging station;
🏡 Guest studio space with full bathroom, kitchenette and private entrance.

90 miles from NYC, the Sylvan's 3.44 acre spread is located at the end of a private road, backing up to woodland. The location is as idyllic as the property itself: surrounded by forest, numerous fishing spots, swimming holes and hiking trails. 

More pics and info, link in bio. Asking $695k. Listed by Erica Keberle and Robin Jones of @catskillmountainhouses.

Open House at 20 Carpathy Court, Glen Spey, NY 12737 on Saturday, March 18, noon-2pm. Please RSVP to robin@catskillmountainhouses.com.

Photos by @catskillimage; staging by @majorjackscatskills.

New in EB real estate: this architect-designed home in Katonah, NY.

Less than 50 miles from NYC, this modern house boasts breathtaking views and abundant natural light ✨ From sunrises to twilight transitions, every moment is illuminated by the glass walls that adorn both the front and back of the property. Features include:

🏠 Three bedroom, three bathroom home;
🌿 2,500 square foot home on .2 acres;
☀️ Living room with fireplace and floor to ceiling windows;
🛏️ Primary bedroom with walk-in custom closets, plus an updated ensuite bath;
💻 Loft space for flexible use, currently an office;
⛲️ Outdoor spaces include stone patio and wood deck with fountain;
🔥 Large family room with additional fireplace.

This modern home is a perfect home base for anyone who needs to be in the city quickly, but enjoys being near the best of the Hudson Valley, within walkable proximity of both Katonah Village and the Katonah MetroNorth Station.

Asking $1,325,000. More pics and info, link in bio.

For showing or inquiries, contact Carine Nowak @westchesterbroker or Cate Bauer @catebauerny with The Carine and Cate Team at 914-582-9898 and/or 914-490-9877, or email carinenowak@compass.com and/or catebauer@compass.com.
24 Ridge Street in Katonah, NY.

New in EB real estate: the Hemp Houses of Stone Ridge, NY 🌿

This enclave of four unique, modern homes will be built using high-performance, non-toxic Isohemp Hempcrete block.

Designed for wellness and low-maintenance living, these stylish houses are made with superior materials of naturally derived or recycled earth-friendly products. The three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom healthy homes are a natural, breathing, humidity regulating, carbon sinking, and mold resistant envelope with high energy performance. 

Features Include: 
🏡 1,800-5,000 square foot, customizable floor plans;
🌳 4+ acre lots;
🔥 High-efficiency inverter heat pump systems;
⭐️ Energy Star Bosch electric appliances;
🔨 Custom cabinetry;
🪟 European triple-glazed windows;
🔺 Standing seam metal roofs;
🚿 High-quality bath fixtures;
✨ Upgrades include an accessory dwelling, shou sugi ban exterior finish, a natural swimming pool, a solarium, and a vegetable garden.

Two parcels at Hemp Houses are available, each with 4.2-4.5 acre lots. Hemp Houses are under 2 hours from Manhattan, 30 minutes to Amtrak at Rhinecliff, and six minutes into the town of Stone Ridge. A complete brochure is available through the listing agent. 

Pricing begins at $1,170,000. For tours, floor, and site plans, contact Leslie Foti @UpstateAbodes, at (917) 670-8509 and Tony Parrotta at (917) 575-0725, at Coldwell Banker Village Green.

Weekend inspiration: embrace nature in style this spring and summer at @killercatmountainhouse in Hunter, NY. 

This 10-person Catskills vacation rental delivers the delightfully unexpected, from Parisian-chic décor and animal prints, to kid-friendly game room with vintage arcade games and ping pong. Plan a wellness morning with yoga on the deck followed by a sauna session, then bask in the warm weather as you enjoy sunsets from the hot tub and stargaze by the fire pit.

Features include:
🏠 Four bedroom, three bathroom home sleeping 10 guests;
⛷️ 5 minutes to Hunter Mountain, less than 15 minutes to Windham Mountain;
⛰️ 900-sq-ft deck with direct Hunter Mountain views;
🔥 Outdoor hot tub, hot-barrel sauna and firepit;
🌿 Living room with fireplace and 16-foot slider for indoor-outdoor enjoyment;
📺 Samsung 55” TV with a wide array of streaming apps;
🎶 Marshall speaker and Crosley record player with vintage record collection;
👩‍🍳 Fully equipped, custom-designed kitchen;
🍴 Dining space for 8 guests;
🏓 Game room with arcade machines, ping pong, darts and board games;
💻 Designated work station with high-speed internet.

This ultra-luxe retreat offers a unique getaway in the Catskills, whether you plan to explore the area or just check-in and "check out." 

Rates begin at $600/night. For availability, check the link in @escape_brooklyn or @killercatmountainhouse bio.

Photos: 1-4, 6, 8-10 by @dirtandglass; 5 by @sunchasemedia.co; 7 by hudsonvalleyhappenings

New in EB real estate: the stunning House on the Cliff is nestled high up a hill on Overlook Mountain on Raycliffe Drive in Woodstock, NY. 

The four bedroom, three bathroom home boasts floor-to-ceiling windows, and an in-ground pool — both of which are perfect spots for taking in the panoramic mountain views.

Features include:
🏠 Four bedroom, three bathroom home on 7.66 acres;
🏊🏼‍♀️ In-ground seasonal pool;
🔥 Living room with 22 foot ceilings, oversize windows and stylish hanging fireplace;
📚 Den/office with fireplace;
🚿 Ensuite primary bedroom with walk-in shower, floor-to-ceiling window & double sinks;
🌳 Landscaped atrium at center of home, visible from living room, kitchen and den;
⛰️ Stunning panoramic views of Overlook Mountain and the surrounding landscapes. 

This contemporary masterpiece is being offered at $2.5m. More pics and info, link in bio.

Listed by Sheena Lepez @upstate_catskills_realtor with Berkshire Hathaway Home Services Hudson Valley Properties. For showings and inquiries, contact 845-616-2509 or sheena.m.lepez@gmail.com.

Photos: @laszloimage & @kate.gos

New in EB real estate: launching 3/29, the Bostock Farm in Shokan, NY. Circa 1910, this home offers the perfect blend of old-world charm and modern amenities set on 2.6 acres. 

Features include:
🏠 Four bedroom, two bathroom home;
🌿 2,288 square foot home on 2.6 acres;
🔥 Airy living room with fireplace connecting to sunroom;
☀️ Sunroom with additional wood burning fireplace;
🪵 Original pine wood floors throughout;
🍴 Open format kitchen with butler’s pantry for storage;
🌲 Outdoor space with fire pit.

The airy Bostock Farm is centrally located near some of the region’s best offerings, from the towns of Olive, Woodstock, and Phoenicia — and five minutes to the Ulster County Rail Trail, where visitors can strech their legs on 11+ miles of trails running alongside the stunning and scenic Ashokan Reservoir. 

More pics and info, link in bio; listing launches on the market 3/29. Asking $699k. 

Listed by @upstateabodes Leslie Foti and Tony Parrota with Coldwell Banker Village Green Realty. 

‼️Open House Saturday, April 1, 2023 from 11:00 am-2:00 pm at 341 Bostock Rd, Shokan, NY 12481.

For inquiries or to RSVP to open house, contact Leslie Foti at 917-670-809/leslie@upstateabodes.com; or Tony Parrota at 917-575-0725.

Weekend inspiration: head to the @urbancowboylodge this spring and dive deep into an indulgent, re-energizing getaway — for the most unique Catskills experience that only the Urban Cowboy can provide ✨

The great outdoors meets rustic luxury at this stunning mountain lodge on 68 acres, whose features include:

🌲 9 suites with outdoor cedar hot tubs for forest bathing;
🛁 12 suites with copper clawfoot tubs with impressive mountain views;
♨️ Estonian sauna for guest use;
🏊🏼‍♀️ Creek frontage for spring cold plunges & summer swims;
